public interface SanitizedModelData

Methods here that are deprecated basically need to be rethought out in light of the new Decorator approach to sanitizing the model data. (e.g. The clients of this, shouldn't care whether we are PCAing or not they should just get the new features, same with transformation of the columns, etc...)
